   * 	// then, when the window resizes, we can re-render at a different scale:
   * 	// first, unstore all our lines:
   * 	myShape.unstore();
   * 	// then cache using the new scale:
   * 	myShape.cache(0,0,500,500,newScale);
   * 	// finally, store the existing commands again:
