	 *     <li>{{#crossLink "AbstractLoader/SOUND:property"}}{{/crossLink}}: Audio file formats</li>
	 *     <li>{{#crossLink "AbstractLoader/SPRITESHEET:property"}}{{/crossLink}}: JSON SpriteSheet definitions. This
